==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Subhumerate
<hw>Sub*hu"mer*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Sub-</er>, <er>Humerus</er>.]</ety> <def>To place the shoulders
under; to bear.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Nothing surer ties a friend than freely to <qex>subhumerate</qex>
the burden which was his.</q> <rj><qau>Feltham.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subhyaloid</ent>⟦br⟧
